Title: 数据流/状态流图
Describe: S07_DATA_OR_STATE_FLOW。说明消息、工具、文档、profile 和配置数据如何在包之间移动。
------------------------------------------------------------
[Example]
Agent 消息状态流

[Description]
Agent 的主要状态是 `messages`，模型输出、工具调用、工具结果和结构化响应都围绕这个状态流转。

[UML]
@startuml
state "Input Messages" as Input
state "ModelRequest" as ModelRequest
state "AIMessage" as AI
state "Tool Calls Pending" as ToolPending
state "ToolMessage Appended" as ToolMessage
state "Structured Response" as Structured
state "Final State" as Final

[*] --> Input
Input --> ModelRequest : create_agent prepares state
ModelRequest --> AI : BaseChatModel returns result
AI --> ToolPending : tool_calls present
ToolPending --> ToolMessage : ToolNode executes tools
ToolMessage --> ModelRequest : 回到模型请求循环
AI --> Structured : response_format required
Structured --> Final : validation succeeds
AI --> Final : no tool_calls and no structured output
Final --> [*]
@enduml

[Detail]
状态图回答“agent state 如何收敛”。循环只在模型要求工具调用时发生；否则直接进入结构化响应校验或终态。失败路径包括 unknown dynamic tools、结构化输出多次返回、Pydantic validation 失败和 provider API 错误。维护者修改 middleware 或 response_format 时，应确认这些状态转换仍然可预测。

------------------------------------------------------------
[Example]
文档与文本切分数据流

[Description]
`langchain-text-splitters` 依赖 Core 的 Document 抽象，把长文本或文档拆成下游检索、索引或 chain 可消费的 chunk。

[UML]
@startuml
left to right direction
component "原始文本 / Document" as Raw
component "TextSplitter\nbase.py:44" as Splitter
component "Document chunks" as Chunks
component "Retriever / VectorStore" as Retrieval
component "Chain / Agent input" as ChainInput

Raw --> Splitter : split_text 或 split_documents
Splitter --> Chunks : chunk_size, overlap, metadata
Chunks --> Retrieval : indexing
Retrieval --> ChainInput : retrieved context
@enduml

[Detail]
`TextSplitter` 位于 `libs/text-splitters/langchain_text_splitters/base.py:44`。它不是模型调用路径的一部分，但支撑 RAG 场景的数据预处理。箭头表示数据转换方向：原始文档被切分、保留 metadata，再进入检索或向量存储。风险主要来自 chunk overlap、HTML/Markdown/JSON 特定切分器和 metadata 传递不一致。

------------------------------------------------------------
[Example]
模型 Profile 数据流

[Description]
`libs/model-profiles` 提供 CLI 刷新 provider profile，生成或更新 partner 包的 `_profiles.py` 数据，用于模型能力判断。

[UML]
@startuml
participant "langchain-profiles CLI" as CLI
participant "Provider source" as ProviderSource
participant "profile_augmentations.toml" as Aug
participant "partner data/_profiles.py" as Profiles
participant "Chat model profile lookup" as Lookup

CLI -> ProviderSource: refresh provider data
CLI -> Aug: apply augmentations
CLI -> Profiles: write generated profiles
Lookup -> Profiles: read capability flags
@enduml

[Detail]
`refresh` 位于 `libs/model-profiles/langchain_model_profiles/cli.py:255`。OpenAI 包中 `_MODEL_PROFILES = cast(ModelProfileRegistry, _PROFILES)`，并通过 `_get_default_model_profile` 读取模型能力。这个数据流影响 structured output、tool use 和上下文窗口判断。风险是 profile 数据过期会让 feature detection 与真实 provider 行为偏离。

